<title>ạ̉nt llsẖfạh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̉nt llsẖfạh rby lḥn ạ̉ngẖạm
 ạlsmạʾ
 ysmw by ạltrnym ḥty̱ tmnḥ ạlnfs ạlʿzạʾ
 ạlqrạr- ḥwạsy klhạ tʿly ṣwthạ wthtf lk
 ạlʿql wạlsẖfạh ạlqlb wạlḥyạẗ ạlkl mlkk
 2- ạ̉nt llʿyn ạ̹lhy mḥwy̱ ṣbḥ fy ẓlạm
